<subSubSection pageId="92" pageNumber="370" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="92.[1454,2662,1204,2062]" pageId="92" pageNumber="370">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1456,1805,1949,1982]" pageId="92" pageNumber="370">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Endangered on The IUCN Red List. Baker’s Harvest Mouse has a restricted distribution, and its forest habitats are decreasing.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
